        <abstract>
            <p>Is staying at a friend’s [T. H. Farrer’s] house for rest until after 6 July, so cannot see CVR at Down.</p> 
<p>Hopes he thanked CVR for the last Report [one of CVR’s <hi rend="italic">Annual reports on the noxious, beneficial and other insects of the State of Missouri</hi> (1868–76)].</p> 
